1-Wire channels must have maintained in PVLng in channel view the

- serial  -- REAL serial as 28CA2307040000E0 - NOT 28.CA2307040000 !
- channel -- the channel to read, e.g. temperature

Needed packages on Debian/Ubuntu:

    sudo apt-get install owfs ow-shell

Change /etc/owfs.conf like this

    # This part must be changed on real installation
    #server: FAKE = DS18S20,DS2405
    #
    # USB device: DS9490
    server: usb = all
